            <div class="col-sm-6 text-left">
              <h1 class="heading1">Where Work Happens</h1>
              <p class="text-left">When your team needs to kick off a project, 
                hire a new employee, deploy some code, review a sales contract, 
                finalize next year's budget, measure an A/B test, 
                plan your next office opening, and more, Slack has you covered.</p>
                <div class="col-sm-7 inputFiled">
                  <input type="email" class="form-control form1" id="email" placeholder="Email Address">
                  <div class="form_error" id="invalid_email">This Email address is not valid</div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-5 buttonField">
                  <button id="submit" type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg button1">Get Started</button>
                </div>
                <div class="question">Already using Slack ? <a href="#">Sign in</a></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
